snippet.title: Pathankot Air Force Base Terror Attack: Watch Major Developments

localized.description:
Pathankot Air Force base terror attack: Watch major developments.

Two terrorists and two soldiers killed in terror attack at Pathankot Air Force Station in Punjab. Pathankot is a key air base for MiG-21 Bison fighters and Mi-35 attack helicopters, located 50 kilometers from Indo-Pak border. The suspected terrorists belong to Jaish-e-Mohammed (JeM) terror outfit.
